M|Over|tx|Bugs often manifest deep in the call stack (git init in wrong directory, file created in wrong location, db opened w/ wrong path). Your instinct is to fix where the er appears, but that's treating a symptom.
M|Over|**Co|** Trace backward through the call chain until you find the original trigger, then fix at the source.
