M|Key |tx|**NEVER fix just where the er appears.** Trace back to find the original trigger.
M|Stac|**In|** Use `console.er()` not logger - logger may be suppressed
M|Stac|**Be|** Log before the dangerous operation, not after it fails
M|Stac|**In|** Directory, cwd, environment variables, timestamps
M|Stac|**Ca|** `new er().stack` shows complete call chain
